[32m+[m[32m## ✨ Features[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### 📊 Advanced Analytics Dashboard[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Real-time Metrics**: Revenue, orders, customers, conversion rates[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Interactive Charts**: Sales trends, revenue by category, order distribution[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Performance KPIs**: Average order value, customer growth, top products[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Date Range Filters**: Custom date ranges for detailed analysis[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Animated Widgets**: Smooth transitions with Framer Motion[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### 📦 Product Management[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Full CRUD Operations**: Create, read, update, delete products[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Bulk Actions**: Update multiple products, bulk delete, status changes[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Advanced Filtering**: Search, category, price range, stock status[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Image Management**: Multiple images per product, drag-and-drop upload[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Stock Tracking**: Real-time inventory, low stock alerts, stock history[m
[32m+[m[32m- **SEO Optimization**: URL slugs, meta descriptions, structured data[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### 🛒 Order Management[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Order Tracking**: Real-time order status updates[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Status Workflow**: Pending → Processing → Shipped → Delivered[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Payment Processing**: Multiple payment methods, payment status tracking[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Order History**: Complete customer order history[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Invoice Generation**: Automatic invoice creation[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Notifications**: Real-time order updates[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### 👥 User & Role Management[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)**: Super Admin, Admin, Manager, User roles[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Permission System**: Granular permissions per role[m
[32m+[m[32m- **User Activity Tracking**: Audit logs for all actions[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Account Management**: Profile updates, password changes[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Team Management**: Invite and manage team members[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### 🔐 Authentication & Security[m
[32m+[m[32m- **JWT Authentication**: Access and refresh token strategy[m
