[32m+[m[32m- **Password Security**: Bcrypt hashing with 12 rounds[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Protected Routes**: Client and server-side route protection[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Rate Limiting**: Prevent brute force attacks[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Security Headers**: Helmet.js for HTTP security[m
[32m+[m[32m- **CORS Configuration**: Controlled cross-origin requests[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Input Validation**: Zod schemas for type-safe validation[m
