[32m+[m[32m- **Premium Design**: Clean, professional SaaS interface[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Dark/Light Theme**: System preference detection, manual toggle[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Responsive Layout**: Mobile-first design, works on all devices[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Smooth Animations**: Framer Motion for delightful interactions[m
